FBIS3-23275 "jptot011__l94091" JPRS-TOT-94-011-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 7 March 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Hamas Warns Settlers To Leave Before 15 March Five-Stage Operation Planned JN0703131594 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 1210 GMT 7 Mar 94 JN0703131594 Paris Radio Monte Carlo Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] The 'Izz-al-Din al-Qassam Battalions, the military wing of the Islamic Resistance Movement, Hamas today addressed a final warning to Jewish settlers to leave their settlements. In a statement distributed in the occupied territories, it set 15 March as the deadline for this evacuation. The statement, which is signed by the command of 'Izz-al-Din al- Qassam Battalions, says that it has decided to reply militarily through five stages, and that each stage will make the Israeli people and settlers weep over their dead.
